Subject: How good is PKZIP 2.0x encryption?
Date: 15 Jul 1994 14:10:36 GMT
Organization: Black Cat Brewery
Lines: 13
Message-ID: <3065cs$khq@news.worldlink.com>
NNTP-Posting-Host: worldlink.com
